cu.explanation_en: Setting AMF IP to unreachable subnet '10.0.0.1' will cause NG interface connection failure and registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: T1a_cp_dl timing parameter has inconsistent range [429, 285] where min > max, causing front-haul synchronization failure.
du.explanation_zh: T1a_cp_dl 定時參數具有不一致的範圍 [429, 285]，其中最小值 > 最大值，導致前傳同步失敗。
